headline: Tennant (TNC) Q1 Earnings Miss Estimates
summary: Tennant (TNC) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of -18.84% and 0.52%, respectively, for the quarter ended March 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
